<div id="page-hiw" class="page">
  <div style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 24px 80px;position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="section-label">// How It Works</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,50px);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1.5px;margin-bottom:8px;">Everything you need to know.</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width:500px;margin-bottom:48px;">A complete breakdown of how campaigns work, how payouts are calculated, and how tracking is automated — for investors and brands.</p>

```
<div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:14px;">// For Investors</div>
<h2 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.8px;margin-bottom:24px;">How investing works</h2>
<div class="hiw-steps">
  <div class="hiw-step"><div class="hiw-num">01</div><div><div class="hiw-title">Create a free account</div><p class="hiw-desc">Sign up in under 2 minutes. No credit card required. Browse all live campaigns before depositing a dollar.</p></div></div>
  <div class="hiw-step"><div class="hiw-num">02</div><div><div class="hiw-title">Browse live campaigns</div><p class="hiw-desc">Each campaign shows projected ROI based on the brand's historical ROAS, total pool size, platform, duration, and the exact revenue share percentage offered to investors. Premium subscribers see campaigns 48 hours before public release.</p></div></div>
  <div class="hiw-step"><div class="hiw-num">03</div><div><div class="hiw-title">Fund a campaign</div><p class="hiw-desc">Invest as little as $10 into any campaign's pool. Funds are held via Stripe until the launch date. If a campaign doesn't hit its funding target, your money is returned in full automatically.</p></div></div>
  <div class="hiw-step"><div class="hiw-num">04</div><div><div class="hiw-title">Watch it run</div><p class="hiw-desc">Your dashboard shows real-time campaign performance. Every sale tracked through the campaign's auto-generated link appears as it happens. Running totals, current earned amount, and estimated payout — all live.</p></div></div>
  <div class="hiw-step"><div class="hiw-num">05</div><div><div class="hiw-title">Automatic payout</div><p class="hiw-desc">When the campaign closes, AdPool calculates your share of the consumer pool (25% of total profit, proportional to your contribution) and deposits it to your wallet automatically. No action needed.</p></div></div>
</div>

<div style="margin:48px 0;">
  <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:14px;">// The Math</div>
  <h2 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.8px;margin-bottom:16px;">How payouts are calculated</h2>
  <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:24px;">A $50 investment in a $10K campaign that generates $30K in sales:</p>
  <div class="math-rows">
    <div class="math-row"><span>Your investment</span><span>$50</span></div>
    <div class="math-row"><span>Total pool size</span><span>$10,000</span></div>
    <div class="math-row"><span>Your pool share</span><span>0.50%</span></div>
    <div class="math-row"><span>Total revenue generated</span><span>$30,000</span></div>
    <div class="math-row"><span>Profit (revenue − ad spend)</span><span class="up">$20,000</span></div>
    <div class="math-row"><span>Consumer pool (25% of profit)</span><span>$5,000</span></div>
    <div class="math-row highlight"><span>Your payout (0.5% of $5,000)</span><span>$25.00 (+50% ROI)</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="margin:48px 0;">
  <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:14px;">// Attribution</div>
  <h2 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.8px;margin-bottom:16px;">Plug & play tracking</h2>
  <div class="benefit-grid" style="margin-top:0;">
    <div class="benefit-card"><div class="benefit-ico">🔗</div><div class="benefit-title">Auto-Generated UTM Links</div><p class="benefit-desc">When a campaign is approved, AdPool automatically generates a unique UTM tracking link. Every click and purchase through that link is attributed to the campaign.</p></div>
    <div class="benefit-card"><div class="benefit-ico">📡</div><div class="benefit-title">Direct API Integration</div><p class="benefit-desc">AdPool connects directly to Meta's Conversions API, TikTok's Events API, and Google Analytics 4. No self-reporting by brands — the platform reads from the ad network directly.</p></div>
    <div class="benefit-card"><div class="benefit-ico">⚡</div><div class="benefit-title">Real-Time Updates</div><p class="benefit-desc">Sale data syncs to your dashboard hourly. You see every attributed sale as it happens, with running totals and projected payout estimates live.</p></div>
    <div class="benefit-card"><div class="benefit-ico">🔒</div><div class="benefit-title">Automatic Payouts</div><p class="benefit-desc">When a campaign closes, the platform calculates every investor's share and deposits payouts to their AdPool wallet. Fully automated — no manual steps.</p></div>
    <div class="benefit-card"><div class="benefit-ico">⭐</div><div class="benefit-title">Premium — $19/mo</div><p class="benefit-desc">48hr early access to every new campaign before public release. Best campaigns fill up in hours — early access is the real edge.</p></div>
    <div class="benefit-card"><div class="benefit-ico">⚖️</div><div class="benefit-title">Legal Structure</div><p class="benefit-desc">AdPool structures all participation as revenue-sharing agreements, not equity or securities. Similar to affiliate marketing programs — you're in a performance-based revenue share.</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

